text: "I learn more when uploading videos" ~ So True. You think you understand a concept until asked for an explanation. I am trying to employ the Feynman Technique (explaining machine Learning concepts to a lay person) in my own videos for my AI channel. It really makes you think. Not as easy as it sounds. Great work!
